# Safety

Never read secrets (`.env*`, keys, cloud credentials), force-push, reset hard,
delete infrastructure/data, pipe network scripts to a shell, bypass hooks, cache
unsafe HTTP mutations, or weaken tests/coverage to pass CI. Escalate production
credentials, Dokploy access, paid services, IP gray areas, and architecture-wide
trade-offs to Nico.
